remarks: Lemma for ~ nodense .  If the birthdays of two distinct surreals are equal, then the ordinal from ~ nodenselem4 is an element of that birthday.  (Contributed by Scott Fenton, 16-Jun-2011.)
statement:
nodenselem5 $p |- ( ( ( A e. No /\ B e. No ) /\ ( ( bday ` A ) = ( bday ` B ) /\ A <s B ) ) -> |^| { a e. On | ( A ` a ) =/= ( B ` a ) } e. ( bday ` A ) ) $.
$d A a $.
$d B a $.
